run(sql="
    select date, round(RTO/Orders * 100,2) as rto_percent, round(Cancelled/Orders * 100,2) as cancelled_percent from(select TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000)) as date, count(distinct subOrderId) as Orders, count(distinct case when shippedStatus='RTO' and rtoDate is not null then subOrderId end) as RTO, count(distinct case when statusCode='CLD' and shipDate is null then subOrderId end) as Cancelled from `all(agCmDump)` where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000))) BETWEEN 1 AND 100 
    group by orderDate order by orderDate)
",1000)
